<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Document</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/index.css" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/7.0.1/css/all.min.css"
      integrity="sha512-2SwdPD6INVrV/lHTZbO2nodKhrnDdJK9/kg2XD1r9uGqPo1cUbujc+IYdlYdEErWNu69gVcYgdxlmVmzTWnetw=="
      crossorigin="anonymous"
      referrerpolicy="no-referrer"
    />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <div class="logo">
          <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/7b92391c-fce4-44d5-84a3-1541c4b73e96.png" alt="logo" />
        </div>
        <div class="navigator">
          <a href="/home">Menu</a>
          <a href="/corporate">Corporate</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/blogs">Blogs</a>
        </div>
        <div class="header-icons">
          <button class="header-order-btn">order now</button>
          <p><i class="fa-solid fa-cart-shopping"></i></p>
          <p>Sign In</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="landing-page">
        <div class="landing-page-content">
          <i style="color: #47d147; font-size: 2rem">we speak fluent food</i>
          <h1>NO MATTER WHICH CORNER OF THE WORLD <span>it's from.</span></h1>
          <p>
            Freshly cooked global food bowls. From Tokyo to Tuscany, authentic
            flavours delivered fresh to your everyday.
          </p>
          <button class="order-btn">
            order now &nbsp;<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
          </button>
          <div class="advantages">
            <p><i class="fa-solid fa-circle"></i>&nbsp;Cooked to Order</p>
            <p><i class="fa-solid fa-circle"></i>&nbsp;Menu Changes Weekly</p>
            <p><i class="fa-solid fa-circle"></i>&nbsp;Everyday Pricing</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="landing-page-img">
          <div class="rating-box">
            <h1>4.1</h1>
            <p>Rating</p>
          </div>
          <img src="album/landingImg.jpg" alt="" id="landingImg" />
          <div class="happy-customer-box">
            <h1>7M+</h1>
            <p>Happy Customers</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="six-promises">
        <div class="promises-title">
          <h1>BOWLS BEYOND <span style="color: #f9ce10">BORDERS</span></h1>
          <p>
            Six promises that make us different. Six reasons to choose global
            flavours for <br />
            your everyday.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="promises-cards">
          <div class="promises-card">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/d7e81079-1ea0-4446-908d-49ee0e9f008c.JPG" alt="promise1" />
            <i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i> 
            <h2>MORE GLOBAL. MORE OFTEN.</h2>
            <p>From Seoul to Sicily, in your weekday bowl.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="promises-card">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/5653bcf5-cbd0-44fe-be5f-92cb23a66da9.jpg" alt="promise2" />
            <i class="fa-solid fa-fire-flame-curved"></i>
            <h2>COOKED FRESH, NOT PREPPED AHEAD.</h2>
            <p>We fire up only after you order.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="promises-card">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/edf1a1f2-5d33-4f75-a094-2d5d1c0752a8.JPG" alt="promise3" />
            <i class="fa-solid fa-leaf"></i>
            <h2>WHOLESOME INGREDIENTS. HONEST ORIGINS.</h2>
            <p>No additives. No nonsense. Just real food.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="promises-card">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/35fabadb-6f5c-4f0b-922f-0c502c8034e2.JPG" alt="promise4" />
             <i class="fa-solid fa-bolt"></i>
            <h2>GLOBAL CUISINE. BUILT FOR BUSY.</h2>
            <p>Busy day? Sticky commute? Our bowls are built for movement.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="promises-card">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/7a727baa-90f7-4619-8264-477cdeff7bf0.jpg" alt="promise5" />
            <i class="fa-regular fa-heart"></i> 
            <h2>EVERYDAY INDULGENCE. THOUGHTFULLY PRICED.</h2>
            <p>Global food shouldn't come with global markups.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="promises-card">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/c62a0e5c-bc14-4df3-b39c-add99a3422d7.jpg" alt="promise6" />
            <i class="fa-regular fa-calendar"></i> 
            <h2>A NEW MENU. EVERY SINGLE WEEK.</h2>
            <p>No reruns. Just new reasons to keep coming back.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="cook-fresh">
        <h1>SEE HOW WE <span>COOK FRESH</span></h1>
        <img src="album/landingImg.jpg" alt="" />
        <div class="cook-fresh-content">
          <div>
            <h2><span>Fresh Ingredients </span></h2>
            <p>Sourced daily from local markets</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2><span>Made to Order</span></h2>
            <p>Cooking starts only after you order</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h2><span>Expert Chefs</span></h2>
            <p>Trained in authentic global cuisines</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="installation-box">
        <div class="installation-box-content">
          <h1>READY TO TASTE THE DIFFERENCE?</h1>
          <p>
            Join thousands who've discovered that world-class flavours belong in
            your everyday — not just special occasions.
          </p>
          <div class="Download-link">
            <button>
              <i class="fa-solid fa-mobile-screen-button"></i>&nbsp; Download App
            </button>
            <button>
              Order Online &nbsp; &nbsp;<i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="installation-box-explaination">
            <p><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="color: white; font-size: 0.6rem;"></i>&nbsp;New menu every week</p>
            <p><i class="fa-solid fa-circle" style="color: white; font-size: 0.6rem;"></i>&nbsp;Everyday pricing</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        <div class="footer-all-links">
          <div class="footer-links-box">
            <img src="https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/foodvista.1/7b92391c-fce4-44d5-84a3-1541c4b73e96.png" alt="" />
            <p style="margin: 15px 0;">
              Bringing you fresh, global cuisine delivered right to your door.
              Every bowl tells a story of flavor, quality, and care.
            </p>
            <div class="social-media">
              <i class="fa-brands fa-instagram"></i>
              <i class="fa-brands fa-facebook-f"></i>
              <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter"></i>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div  class="footer-links-box">
            <h2>Quick Links</h2>
            <a href="">Menu</a>
            <a href="">Locations</a>
            <a href="">About Us</a>
            <a href="">Corporate Ordering</a>
            <a href="">Bulk Order</a>
            <a href="">Blogs</a>
          </div>
          <div  class="footer-links-box">
            <h2>Support</h2>
            <a href="">Returns & Refunds</a>
            <a href="">Privacy Policy</a>
            <a href="">Terms</a>
          </div>
          <div  class="footer-links-box">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <div>
              <div class="footer-contact-us">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>
                <p>
                  Freshmenu, Sri Vaaru
                  Plaza, Ground Floor, 19th Main Road Next to ProBike HSR Layout
                  1st sector Bangalore 560102
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="footer-contact-us">
                <i class="fa-regular fa-envelope"></i>
                <div class="email-links">
                  <p class="email">order@freshmenu.com</p>
                  <p class="email">grievance@freshmenu.com</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p>Office Hours:</p>
            <p>Monday - Friday (9:00 AM - 6:00 PM)</p>
          </div>
        </div>


        <div class="footer-rights">
          <p>
            &copy;2026 TheFoodTruck. All rights reserved. Made with ❤️ for food lovers
            everywhere.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </body>
</html>
